name: WALLY STEWART
text: “EXCELLENT FOOD AND EXCELLENT SERVICE AND EXCELLENT PRICES. SECOND BEST PIZZA PLACE IN MANCHESTER CLAY COUNTY KENTUCKY.”

name: Jessey Chaffin
text: Substituted stuffed crazy bread with regular, and forgot a 2 liter

name: Gayle Lewis
text: Truly the best 5.00 meal ever! The extra most bestest pizza rocks in taste and value. This is a great clean friendly fast food!

name: R. D. Bob Dylan
text: Best bang for your buck. I worked here for a couple of yrs. and know from experience that the crew here is one of the cleanest in clay county.

name: Brooke Saunders
text: It took forever just to get four pizzas. Only one specialty pizza and I called ahead. 30 minutes late for my mom's birthday party because of these jokes.

name: Tim S. Intense420
text: Very friendly people BUT it's the blandest plastic cheese and sauce. Get new supplier bring me a pizza with Max toppings & extra cheesy and I will consider my loss forgiven plus give 5 stars for the improved taste!

name: Tammy Lunsford
text: Not a good place for kids to work. They are rude to them. Instead of encouraging and teaching them, they discipline them by not letting them work or putting them on the schedule because they didn’t know how to do something that wasn’t taught to them in orientation. Especially one of the managers. Not happy with this place.

name: Lynsey Bryan Bowling
text: Good business establishment, but I really don't like LC sauce.

name: Katherine Jones
text: I miss them in Manchester KY
